{"tid":312046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有片］中共官員視察湖南洪災 扮暈 秘書撐傘食檳榔 醜態畢現","createTime":"2017-07-07T06:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T10:13:47.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b96456fef51799962dcb7acf482717b605f9340","tid":312046,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:05:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=_Z6S0gSOF70&amp;itct=CBIQpDAYACITCJzGjaa_9tQCFYWVWAodSaYLnDIHcmVsYXRlZEjp-rPXk-WOgbsB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_Z6S0gSOF70%26itct%3DCBIQpDAYACITCJzGjaa_9tQCFYWVWAodSaYLnDIHcmVsYXRlZEjp-rPXk-WOgbsB&d=nzlhID8IMPChWPj6qZBcB04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=8c88a4ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=_Z6S0gSOF70&amp;itct=CBIQpDAYACITCJzGjaa_9tQCFYWVWAodSaYLnDIHcmVsYXRlZEjp-rPXk-WOgbsB</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/140156_10bdd11ac40213dfe456fa6325c66cc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F140156_10bdd11ac40213dfe456fa6325c66cc3.jpg&h=bf52acbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/140156_460b83ad2282b3c8726fb7c0e37825ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F140156_460b83ad2282b3c8726fb7c0e37825ab.jpg&h=5c915be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【看中國2017年7月6日訊】湖南連日遭遇強降雨，引發嚴重洪災。大陸民眾批評政府隱瞞災情、救災不力的聲音越來越大。當地官媒發布一名女社區書記在抗洪第一線暈倒的消息，被網民揭造假。此外，長沙市望城區的官員在勘查災情時吃檳榔抽煙，並由女秘書打傘的視頻在網上流傳。<br />\n<br />\n據自由亞洲電臺7月5日報導，湖南洪災期間，中共官方連日發動宣傳機器讚揚救災成果。當地官媒湖南在線報導稱，長沙伍家嶺街道科大佳園社區女書記傅佳，防汛值守連續3個日夜沒休息，終於暈倒在河堤。她醒後第一句話就說:「湘江水退了嗎？快扶我回去，我要繼續盯著。」<br />\n  <br />\n不過，在報導的照片中，傅佳的衣服光鮮乾淨，鞋子也一塵不染。照片上傳網路後，不少人炮轟該名書記是在「作秀」、「擺拍」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民諷刺道：「導演差勁！給點小建議：下次拍照前，先到泥湯裡去打個滾。另外，說完台詞後，別忘了現場交黨費。」<br />\n<br />\n轉發照片的李女士告訴自由亞洲說，中共政府想欺騙老百姓，不料擺拍穿幫，適得其反。<br />\n <br />\n記者就此致電伍家嶺街道辦，一名負責人指傅佳醒來後又堅持到河堤上工作了。當被問到民眾對於「擺拍」的質疑時，對方則解釋稱，當地沒有洪水，所以傅佳的衣褲都很乾淨。而對於為何三天三夜都沒有人替換傅佳？對方則表示要記者直接找傅佳瞭解。但傅佳的電話則一直無人接聽。<br />\n<br />\n此外，7月5日，網上流傳一段長沙市望城區靖港鎮救災現場的視頻，該鎮視察的一名幹部一邊嘴裡嚼著檳榔，一邊抽著煙，其身後是女秘書撐著傘擋雨<br />\n<br />\n有網民質問道：有你這樣抗洪救災的嗎？一個小小的鎮長如此流氓！還指望他們能幹什麼？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.secretchina.com/news/b5/2017/07/06/828330.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F828330.html&d=nzlhID8IMPChWPj6qZBcB04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=ea4014e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.secretchina.com/news/b5/2017/07/06/828330.html</a>"},{"pid":"389d1f24c362e48501d8f516daf4665874427409","tid":312046,"uid":22876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:11:56.000Z","msg":"湖南洞庭湖草頭鄉"},{"pid":"6530de05f825232021163be45d1ee95da892879a","tid":312046,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"記得交黨費呀屌你老母:o"},{"pid":"a13234ef90177ef2596f560248db0a3aa179e970","tid":312046,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:15:07.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"da558feb047318f0f38b228716327cdfd41e5430","tid":312046,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:17:57.000Z","msg":"呢班村幹部<br />\n一個月至少貪污袋過百萬啊屌你"},{"pid":"575a90eaceebbd8b047201337d16af3d3f18b721","tid":312046,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"你還有黨嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5c11004fb461550861ea8c0c10482de97a48d3","tid":312046,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"其實洪水有無得搞???"},{"pid":"bb5bec7073cfb8969fde49af60aa5d349e83088f","tid":312046,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實洪水有無得搞???</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n減少水土流失應該會好啲"},{"pid":"9067462d92f14d4c31d778cf07b914e2fc840191","tid":3120